Add HTTP support to dtool for read only access to datasets
==========================================================

.. |dtool| image:: https://github.com/jic-dtool/dtool-http/blob/master/icons/22x22/dtool_logo.png?raw=True
    :height: 20px
    :target: https://github.com/jic-dtool/dtool-http
